## Performance Optimization Strategies

### Image Optimization
1. Use Next.js `Image` component with automatic optimization
2. Implement responsive images with `srcSet`
3. Use modern formats (WebP with fallbacks)
4. Implement lazy loading for below-the-fold images
5. Generate different sizes for different breakpoints

### Code Splitting
1. Dynamic imports for heavy components
2. Route-based code splitting (automatic with App Router)
3. Component-level code splitting with `next/dynamic`
4. Lazy load third-party scripts

### Caching Strategy
1. Browser caching (Cache-Control headers)
2. CDN caching for static assets
3. Server-side caching with ISR
4. API response caching with fetch options
5. Tag-based revalidation for updates

### Database Queries
1. Implement pagination for large datasets
2. Use filtering and search efficiently
3. Implement caching for frequently accessed data
4. Use database indexes properly
5. Monitor slow queries

